text: Brož in 2017 Lukáš Brož (, born October 23, 1985 in Jablonec nad Nisou) is a Czech luger who has competed since 2000. He finished 16th in the men's doubles event at the 2006 Winter Olympics in Turin. Brož finish 19th in the men's doubles event at the 2007 FIL World Luge Championships in Igls.
